<body lang=3D"EN-NZ" link=3D"#467886" vlink=3D"#96607D" style=3D"word-wrap:=
break-word">
<div class=3D"WordSection1">
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Good afternoon Raffaella<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Your privacy request was received on the 1 July 2025=
 and sent to you by our Privacy Team on the 25 July 2025 and again on the 2=
8 August 2025.<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">The complete file up to that date was sent to you.<o=
:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><b><span lang=3D"EN-US"><br>
</p>
<p style=3D"font-family:Calibri;font-size:10pt;color:#000000;margin:5pt;fon=
t-style:normal;font-weight:normal;text-decoration:none;" align=3D"Center">
Classification: Sensitive<br>
</p>
From:</span></b><span lang=3D"EN-US"> Raffaella del Prete &lt;<a href=3D"ma=
ilto:raffaellanz@icloud.com">raffaellanz@icloud.com</a>&gt;
<br>
<b>Sent:</b> Tuesday, 1 July 2025 11:32 pm</span><o:p></o:p>
<p></p>
<ol start=3D"1" type=3D"1">
<li class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-=
alt:auto;margin-left:-3.8pt;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo3">
<strong><i><span style=3D"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif">Privacy=
 Act Request &#8211; Full Claim Files:</span></i></strong><i><br>
Under the&nbsp;<strong><span style=3D"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-se=
rif">Privacy Act 2020</span></strong>, I formally request a&nbsp;<strong><s=
pan style=3D"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif">full copy of my file=
</span></strong>&nbsp;for both claims (C90306048 and&nbsp;C90306256). This =
includes
 all internal notes, reports, third-party correspondence, scopes, assessmen=
ts, emails, and any other material Tower holds in relation to these claims.=
<o:p></o:p></i></li></ol>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">The Privacy team has handed on to me the below reque=
st from you.<o:p></o:p></p>
<ul type=3D"disc">
<li class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-=
alt:auto;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo6">
<span lang=3D"EN-US">Call recordings/transcripts &amp; communications: Plea=
se include any call recordings or transcripts, text/SMS or instant messages=
, video calls, any other forms of communication, and notes from face-to-fac=
e meetings.</span><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-NZ"=
><o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"mso-margin-top-alt=
:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo6">
<span lang=3D"EN-US">Simple document index: A single list of everything hel=
d on the file (date, author, short description) so I can confirm I&#8217;ve=
 received the lot.<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"m=
so-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo6">
<span lang=3D"EN-US">Redaction reasons: Where something truly can&#8217;t b=
e provided, a short reason and, if possible, a partially released copy with=
 only the sensitive bits removed.<o:p></o:p></span></li></ul>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-a=
lt:auto"><span lang=3D"EN-US">Call recordings: These were not included in y=
our first request as there was no request for them.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-a=
lt:auto"><span lang=3D"EN-US">Simple document index: All documents that rel=
ate to your personal information, that are held on your claim file were upl=
oaded to the sharefolder for you.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-a=
lt:auto"><span lang=3D"EN-US">You should have received: House - FENZ Report=
, 2 Assessor reports and claim file notes upto 24 July 2025.&nbsp; Contents=
 &#8211; Asset Restore SOW and claim file notes.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">The Privacy Act 2020 establishes the guidelines for =
disclosing personal information. Personal information is any information wh=
ich tells us something about a specific individual or have the potential to=
 do so.<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Redaction reasons; &nbsp;to protect the privacy of o=
ther individuals, company information, that isn&#8217;t your personal infor=
mation.<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">I note you now have a further Privacy request dated =
10 September 2025, I will aim to have the file ready to send to you as soon=
 as possible but by the 8 October 2025 at the latest.<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">I will now include all the recorded calls we have on=
 file from you to your claims manager.<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Assessor reports from the 24 July 2025 and claim fil=
e notes from 24 July 2025.<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"line-height:150%"><b><span style=3D"font-si=
ze:10.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif;color=
:#001272;mso-fareast-language:EN-NZ">Regards</span></b><b><span style=3D"fo=
nt-size:10.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif;=
color:#001272;mso-ligatures:none;mso-fareast-language:EN-NZ"><o:p></o:p></s=
pan></b></p>
